Review
  Review: PASS
  The article is a high-quality, professional guide that successfully bridges the gap between sales and customer success
for an enterprise audience. It hits the requested differentiators like the RACI matrix and compliance modules 
effectively, though it requires expansion in the latter half to meet the target word count and depth expectations.
  Strengths:
    + The RACI matrix is a standout feature that provides immediate, high-level value for operational leaders.
    + Strong handling of regulated industry needs (SOC2, HIPAA, BAA) which distinguishes this from generic onboarding 
content.
    + The 'Aha Moment' is correctly framed as a business outcome (T3 model) rather than a simple feature login.
    + Authoritative and professional tone that speaks directly to the 'Enterprise' persona without unnecessary fluff.
